============================================================= presents

                       GTA: London 1969 + 1961

======================================================================

This package contains both GTA: London 1969 and GTA: London 1961. The
  base London 1969 version has been taken from the popular freeloader
  version, and modified with a normal no-CD from GameCopyWorld. 1961,
  however, has been cracked with a custom no-CD by me, found by diff-
  ing the 1969 original EXE to the 1969 cracked EXE, and applying the
  hex changes to the 1961 version. You won't find a cracked 1961 any-
  where else ;-)

-- Information

Just run the version you like from the GTAWIN directory, both will do
  what you expect. The DOS version is not included, as nobody uses 
  DOS anymore. The system requirements are the same as the Classics
  version of GTA1, with probably the same incompatiblities. Note that
  this one does work on Vista. :)
